                          "The Riddle"
               
           
            <lg part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
               <l enjamb="no">
                  <rs type="Color">White</rs> men’s children spread over the earth—</l>
               <l enjamb="no">A <rs type="Color">rainbow</rs> suspending the drawn swords of birth,</l>
               <l enjamb="no">Uniting and blending the races in one</l>
               <l enjamb="no">The world man—cosmopolite—everyman’s son!</l>
            </lg>
            <lg part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
               <l enjamb="no">He channels the stream of the <rs type="Color">red blood and blue,</rs>
               </l>
               <l enjamb="no"> Behold him! A Triton—the peer of the two;</l>
               <l enjamb="no"> Unriddle this riddle of “outside in”</l>
               <l enjamb="no">
                  <rs type="Color">White</rs> men’s children in <rs type="Color">black</rs> men’s skin.</l>
            </lg>
         </p>
         <byline>-Georgia Douglas Johnson</byline>
